      "instruction": "<p>While the spring greens are cooking, combine your <strong>smooth</strong> <strong>peanut butter </strong>with your <strong>honey </strong>and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>tamari soy sauce</strong>, the <strong>pickling juice</strong> from the cucumber and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> then mix everything together – this is your <strong>peanut sauce</strong></p>",
